data.name: theText.Text
data.value: Welcome to Word Detective! Here, you can track along with the voice, or just have it read to you (tracking is more fun!). Right click to load a text file or search Project Gutenberg's free ebooks, or just type straight into the box. Choose how much help you want with the Options, and use the buttons at the top to start, stop, pause, and resume. Have fun!
